short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Webbu is your assistant for the browser

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Webbu is an assistant for your browser. Just like Alexa, ask it to do anything. It will go around the web with you, helping make things a bit better and more convenient.

Examples:
"Make the background blue"
"Whats the time?"
"make column c bold"


Because everyone has different needs, anyone can teach skills to webbu and the code is
open-source.
